Description:

Perfect Day is the second studio album released by German Eurodance act Cascada. It features a number of cover songs and In the first week of UK sales, Perfect Day sold 50,000 copies, debuting at number 12 on the UK album chart. However, in the second week it sold 100,000 copies, but fell to number 16.
